J&uuml;rgen Klopp has cast further doubt on Simon Mignolet&rsquo;s future at Liverpool by suggesting the Belgian will not be selected for Liverpool&rsquo;s Champions League match against Porto on Wednesday.<br />
<br />
Klopp: &ldquo;To be honest I have not made the final decision but it is not the same situation as it was. A good one will play. But I haven&rsquo;t made the decision so far.&rdquo;

Ward: &ldquo;That&rsquo;s what we&rsquo;ve been doing and we&rsquo;ll continue to work that way that. Ultimately the manager has the choice of who plays and we all respect his decisions.&rdquo;<br />
<br />
Ward:  &ldquo;No-one envisaged the rotation policy but the manager has his way of dealing with these things. We all respect it and we&rsquo;re all professional and get on with the job.&rdquo;

